-- Resolved: Module dependencies modeled as DependencyHealthCheck[] on ModuleManifest.
-- Modules declare their external service dependencies with health endpoints.
-- Dependencies affect health status derivation (DependencyHealthDegradation rule)
-- and are visible in the ModuleHealthOverview surface.
-- Full module-to-module runtime dependencies (e.g., CareerBERT → AI module for embeddings)
-- will extend this mechanism when needed — the DependencyHealthCheck value type can be
-- promoted to a ModuleDependency that references registered modules by ID.

-- Resolved: manifestVersion: Integer added to ModuleManifest (all modules start at 1)

